<lb n="5"/>mutta vaṭaṅkaṇṭu kākkilaṉ kāṭavar koṉeṇapaṭṭa ceṉaiyetir paṭ 
<lb n="6"/>ṭoḻuka veḻunta puṇṇar viṇpaṭṭalaiyppaṭai toṭṭa cuntara
<lb n="7"/>miṉavaṉe poṉ
